org.sql: SELECT members.* FROM members INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = members.project_id WHERE members.user_id = "$1" AND projects.status <> "$2" AND members.project_id IS NULL ORDER BY members.id ASC LIMIT "$3"

rewrites.sql: SELECT members.* FROM members INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = members.project_id WHERE members.user_id = "$1" AND projects.status <> "$2" AND False ORDER BY members.id ASC LIMIT "$3"
SELECT members.* FROM members WHERE members.user_id = "$1" AND False ORDER BY members.id ASC LIMIT "$3"
SELECT members.* FROM members WHERE members.user_id = "$1" AND members.project_id IS NULL ORDER BY members.id ASC LIMIT "$3"
